Untold Legends, the first DLC of Daedalic Entertainment''s successful turn-based strategy RPG Blackguards, continues the main story line with seven new exciting quests. Fight against rebellious slaves, learn more about Takate''s past and stop sinister magic rituals.', 0, null);

