Hiding from the Zombies in abandoned buildings, they build blockades, set traps and – as a last resort – use weapons to fight.', 0, '2011-07-05');

Play the campaign in single-player, local co-op or online co-op with a friend. Make your way through the levels with a huge variety of weapons. Use assault rifles, shotguns, grenades, mini-guns and a lot more to unlock during the game.', 0, '2011-06-02');

