• Lucky wheel. Even in the aftermath you still get a door to door salesmen knocking at the fortress gates. Earn or buy a spin on the lucky wheel to win a gift. Take a risk, after all, and it’s not like things could get any worse.
• Kill the flying zombie. Yes, that''s right, flying. What?! Have you never seen a zombie with a jetpack before? Catch them in flight, you never know, they just may drop something.
• Go Global. Connect with friends online and gain a bonus increase productivity. Invite them to rooms to rebuild faster and stronger.

